# Private Knowledge Base — Project Context

AI-powered personal knowledge operations system. Local-first Docker Compose MVP.

## Normative stack (do not substitute without ADR)

- Python 3.12+, FastAPI, Pydantic v2, SQLAlchemy 2.x, Alembic
- PostgreSQL + pgvector, Neo4j Community, Redis + Celery
- LangGraph, Next.js + TypeScript
- Structured JSON logs, OpenTelemetry-compatible tracing

## Current phase

**Phase 2 — Parsing and retrieval foundation** (Phase 1 complete).

Next: chunking, embeddings, pgvector search, source preview. Then Phase 3 knowledge proposals.

